title: Worst Date Wednesday: He Messed Himself at the Mall
description: A listener tells us the story of a guy who wanted to take her out for her birthday and "show her how a woman is supposed to be treated".  It all begins with a trip to the mall where he disappeared for a while and when she found him again, she couldn't believe what he had done.  The ending of this date is what's the MOST surprising.
